WEBVTT

01:31.060 --> 01:35.000
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.880 --> 01:39.130
[2002]

01:37.200 --> 01:37.870
Sir.

01:38.560 --> 01:39.680
I'll take a Grade 9 English

01:39.680 --> 01:40.610
listening tape.

01:40.759 --> 01:41.200
Got it.

01:41.229 --> 01:42.430
I'll find one for you.

01:51.120 --> 01:51.789
Found it.

01:54.400 --> 01:55.560
"Back to the Past"?

01:56.400 --> 01:57.759
I wrote it wrong in a rush.

01:57.759 --> 01:59.229
It should be "Back to the Future."

01:59.229 --> 02:00.430
That's a classic movie

02:00.430 --> 02:01.120
made in 1985.

02:01.120 --> 02:01.920
It's really good.

02:01.920 --> 02:02.680
You want a disk of it?

02:02.680 --> 02:04.280
I'd rather go back to the past

02:05.430 --> 02:06.920
than the future.

02:08.729 --> 02:11.009
[Episode 11: The Foreshadowing of Fate]

02:13.000 --> 02:14.870
Alright, come on in!

02:17.870 --> 02:18.870
What do you think?

02:20.310 --> 02:21.470
It's well decorated.

02:21.470 --> 02:22.430
-All of these...
-Wei.

02:22.430 --> 02:22.910
were installed by me.

02:22.910 --> 02:24.520
You've created quite a cozy space.

02:24.520 --> 02:25.630
No doubt.

02:25.710 --> 02:26.710
You should join Uncle Yong

02:26.710 --> 02:28.310
in his home improvement business.

02:28.310 --> 02:29.190
No, no, no.

02:29.190 --> 02:31.520
I prefer to be a street vendor
with Sis Bai.

02:33.590 --> 02:35.120
You paged each and every one of us

02:35.120 --> 02:36.250
just to show us this?

02:36.310 --> 02:37.240
Of course.

02:37.240 --> 02:38.280
See, I've even prepared

02:38.280 --> 02:39.360
drinks for you guys.

02:39.360 --> 02:39.960
Look,

02:39.960 --> 02:41.910
in this skyscraper-filled city
of Shengcheng,

02:41.910 --> 02:42.680
there is a small space

02:42.680 --> 02:43.800
exclusive to us.

02:44.240 --> 02:44.870
How very nice.

02:44.870 --> 02:45.680
I feel like the whole city

02:45.680 --> 02:46.430
is mine now.

02:46.870 --> 02:48.870
I don't need to own the entire Shengcheng.

02:48.870 --> 02:50.360
All I hope for is to build a home here

02:50.360 --> 02:51.490
as soon as possible.

02:53.150 --> 02:55.360
Neither am I asking for much.

02:56.000 --> 02:58.470
I just want a store.

02:58.470 --> 02:59.590
All deities up there,

02:59.590 --> 03:01.710
bless me with a rented store.

03:02.120 --> 03:03.030
What about you, Xiaolan?

03:03.030 --> 03:04.760
What do you want in Shengcheng?

03:05.760 --> 03:06.550
Me?

03:07.250 --> 03:09.210
I want to run freely,

03:09.470 --> 03:10.400
lead a good life,

03:10.910 --> 03:11.710
and...

03:12.000 --> 03:13.060
make a lot of money!

03:13.590 --> 03:14.390
That's right.

03:14.540 --> 03:16.210
Make a lot of money!

03:16.240 --> 03:17.300
Make a lot of money!

03:17.470 --> 03:18.430
Lead a good life!

03:18.910 --> 03:20.030
-Come on.
-Come on.

03:20.150 --> 03:24.310
Lead a good life, and make a lot of money!

03:26.560 --> 03:27.910
How about taking a full set of sizes

03:27.910 --> 03:28.400
for each color

03:28.400 --> 03:29.800
of these three plaid shirts?

03:29.800 --> 03:30.120
Sounds nice.

03:30.120 --> 03:30.470
Deal?

03:30.560 --> 03:30.890
Deal.

03:31.360 --> 03:32.400
This blue shirt,

03:32.630 --> 03:35.310
and these striped ones...

03:35.680 --> 03:36.710
I'll give you a discount on them,

03:36.710 --> 03:37.280
alright?

03:37.590 --> 03:38.790
Take a few more pieces

03:38.870 --> 03:39.840
of Size S and Size M,

03:39.840 --> 03:40.310
okay?

03:40.430 --> 03:42.160
T-These two sizes sell better.

03:42.310 --> 03:42.750
Okay.

03:43.030 --> 03:43.800
Alright. I'll take these.

03:43.800 --> 03:44.750
The same address, right?

03:44.750 --> 03:45.570
I'll pack them up now.

03:45.570 --> 03:46.090
Okay.

03:46.120 --> 03:47.180
Thanks. Take care!

03:47.310 --> 03:49.079
Sometimes at the back of my mind,
there's a worry

03:49.079 --> 03:50.630
about whether an opportunity

03:50.630 --> 03:52.360
or an accident will come first.

03:54.960 --> 03:55.590
Ms. Xia!

03:58.430 --> 03:59.660
Why just look at me?

04:00.120 --> 04:01.120
Look at the goods.

04:02.150 --> 04:03.030
Both merchandise

04:03.030 --> 04:05.430
and merchants need observing in business.

04:06.710 --> 04:07.190
Right.

04:08.080 --> 04:09.400
Only qualified merchandise
and competent merchants

04:09.400 --> 04:10.910
can make for long-lasting business.

04:10.910 --> 04:12.470
Don't you worry. My goods here

04:12.470 --> 04:13.590
are all for foreign trade.

04:13.590 --> 04:15.050
Their quality is assured.

04:15.560 --> 04:17.019
As for me, the merchant...

04:17.829 --> 04:19.160
Promises are of no use.

04:19.269 --> 04:20.310
You'll know what I'm like

04:20.310 --> 04:21.570
when you get to know me.

04:24.190 --> 04:25.250
Take a look around.

04:29.800 --> 04:30.430
Mr. Chen.

04:31.210 --> 04:33.120
Which countries do you usually go to

04:33.120 --> 04:34.310
for foreign trade?

04:34.750 --> 04:36.610
Do they include the Soviet Union?

04:36.720 --> 04:37.720
The Soviet Union...

04:37.720 --> 04:38.580
Yes, I go there.

04:38.720 --> 04:39.600
Besides that,

04:39.600 --> 04:41.800
I'd also travel to many other places
like Europe

04:41.800 --> 04:42.460
and the U.S.

04:43.800 --> 04:44.630
If changes were

04:44.630 --> 04:45.920
to happen to the Soviet Union,

04:45.920 --> 04:47.780
would your business be affected?

04:48.120 --> 04:49.000
If there were changes,

04:49.000 --> 04:50.930
my business would certainly be...

04:54.190 --> 04:55.790
Changes in the Soviet Union?

04:56.220 --> 04:57.820
What changes could there be?

04:59.190 --> 05:01.000
He has no idea of that big historic event.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.530
He can't be a time traveler.

05:03.490 --> 05:05.310
Whether its economy gets better or worse,

05:05.310 --> 05:06.970
there will be impacts, right?

05:08.000 --> 05:09.060
You mean that, huh?

05:09.430 --> 05:10.030
It's true.

05:10.480 --> 05:11.410
But don't worry.

05:11.650 --> 05:12.730
I'm a businessman

05:12.830 --> 05:13.630
of integrity.

05:13.830 --> 05:15.480
Whatever changes there may be
in that region,

05:15.480 --> 05:16.450
there's no way I will expose

05:16.450 --> 05:18.580
my customers to any negative effects.

05:19.160 --> 05:20.510
Thank you then, Mr. Chen.

05:20.510 --> 05:21.170
No problem.

05:22.600 --> 05:23.870
Does this polo shirt

05:24.000 --> 05:25.200
come in other colors?

05:25.220 --> 05:25.700
Yes.

05:26.750 --> 05:27.510
Wait a moment.

05:27.510 --> 05:28.090
I'll get them for you.

05:28.090 --> 05:28.440
Okay.

05:29.240 --> 05:31.170
Check out other items, if you will.

05:57.830 --> 05:58.360
Hold on.

05:58.920 --> 05:59.560
Granny Yu.

06:00.040 --> 06:02.120
The rent you gave me yesterday...

06:02.360 --> 06:03.430
I mean this ten-yuan bill.

06:03.430 --> 06:04.430
It's too worn out.

06:04.720 --> 06:05.920
I'd like a better one.

06:06.320 --> 06:07.150
Not a problem.

06:11.160 --> 06:12.160
Sorry about that.

06:13.190 --> 06:14.950
Is this one okay?

06:17.830 --> 06:19.070
I'm leaving then.

06:24.680 --> 06:25.680
Alright, thanks.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.240
Check it out.

06:48.240 --> 06:49.300
Not one is missing.

06:49.600 --> 06:50.480
I'll send them to the same

06:50.480 --> 06:51.480
old address, okay?

06:51.480 --> 06:51.830
Okay.

06:52.220 --> 06:54.420
The package will be out this afternoon.

06:55.360 --> 06:55.960
Oh, right!

06:56.750 --> 06:57.630
Next time when you come,

06:57.630 --> 06:58.510
you won't have to walk all the way in.

06:58.510 --> 07:00.830
I'm planning to move to that stall

07:00.950 --> 07:02.270
right by the entrance.

07:03.870 --> 07:05.190
Are you moving to a larger stall

07:05.190 --> 07:07.000
because you've made big money, Mr. Chen?

07:07.000 --> 07:07.950
I wouldn't put it that way.

07:07.950 --> 07:08.950
I'm still counting on you

07:08.950 --> 07:10.770
and other patrons to support my business.

07:10.770 --> 07:11.480
This is the main reason

07:11.480 --> 07:12.540
for the move, look.

07:13.800 --> 07:15.310
I have a batch of trench coats

07:15.310 --> 07:16.370
piling up in stock.

07:16.480 --> 07:17.740
If I don't put in some effort

07:17.740 --> 07:18.360
and sell them off

07:18.360 --> 07:19.510
this autumn, I'll have trouble

07:19.510 --> 07:21.390
replenishing supplies next time.

07:21.390 --> 07:22.360
That's why I'm planning

07:22.360 --> 07:24.040
to move to that stall by the entrance

07:24.040 --> 07:25.300
for more foot traffic.

07:25.360 --> 07:26.510
This trench coat of yours

07:26.510 --> 07:28.310
is nice both in style and fabric.

07:28.830 --> 07:30.430
But the design is too ahead of time,

07:30.430 --> 07:31.510
and the price is too high.

07:31.510 --> 07:32.750
No customers would opt for it.

07:32.750 --> 07:33.630
They're afraid that if they buy any,

07:33.630 --> 07:35.159
they'll end up stuck with them
without a sale.

07:35.159 --> 07:36.190
Moving to a new stall

07:36.190 --> 07:37.990
won't help you sell these coats.

07:39.510 --> 07:41.020
Is there a string you can pull?

07:41.020 --> 07:41.920
Don't deny it.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.000
Given what you said,

07:43.000 --> 07:44.659
I'm sure you can pull a string.

07:45.390 --> 07:46.390
It's not a string.

07:46.560 --> 07:47.690
But I do have an idea.

07:48.159 --> 07:48.870
What idea?

07:49.390 --> 07:51.250
Go ask some magazine publishers.

07:51.600 --> 07:53.390
If these coat can get on a magazine,

07:53.390 --> 07:55.390
there won't be worries about sales.

07:56.480 --> 07:57.480
Advertisements.

07:57.750 --> 07:59.810
Are you suggesting I advertise them?

07:59.870 --> 08:00.920
Yes, sort of.

08:01.340 --> 08:02.540
Something like that.

08:02.680 --> 08:04.280
I mean apparel sponsorship.

08:06.390 --> 08:07.160
Ms. Xia...

08:07.920 --> 08:08.390
No.

08:08.560 --> 08:09.620
Respected Ms. Xia,

08:09.800 --> 08:10.270
look,

08:10.510 --> 08:11.830
tomorrow, I'll do as you say.

08:11.830 --> 08:13.560
If it works out, you'll receive

08:13.870 --> 08:15.130
a share of the profits.

08:15.720 --> 08:16.800
No need for that.

08:16.950 --> 08:17.390
I'm leaving.

08:17.390 --> 08:17.720
Okay.

08:17.920 --> 08:18.520
Take care.

08:23.120 --> 08:23.800
Mom!

08:25.600 --> 08:26.920
Mom, I'm back!

08:28.920 --> 08:29.800
Stop shouting.

08:30.950 --> 08:32.039
Remember the rules?

08:32.039 --> 08:33.280
Sorry, Granny Yu.

08:33.360 --> 08:34.559
I didn't see you here.

08:34.750 --> 08:35.440
I promise

08:35.549 --> 08:37.210
I won't shout like that again.

08:38.240 --> 08:39.370
Oh right, Granny Yu,

08:39.510 --> 08:40.720
last time, I noticed your blouse

08:40.720 --> 08:42.120
was torn by a tree branch.

08:42.240 --> 08:43.650
So I brought a new one for you

08:43.650 --> 08:44.840
from my procurement trip to Longcheng.

08:44.840 --> 08:45.510
Take a look.

08:55.030 --> 08:57.480
I didn't ask you to buy me a new blouse.

08:58.670 --> 08:59.480
I was just...

09:00.080 --> 09:01.080
planning to spend

09:02.120 --> 09:03.520
ten yuan buying a new one.

09:04.840 --> 09:06.570
If you think it's a loss for you,

09:06.870 --> 09:08.400
then take this blouse back.

09:09.480 --> 09:10.680
Thank you for the pay.

09:10.870 --> 09:11.820
Keep the blouse.

09:12.510 --> 09:14.710
I'll leave you to it and go upstairs now.

09:18.000 --> 09:18.860
Your mother...

09:19.840 --> 09:21.960
was picked up by a car.

09:22.870 --> 09:25.910
A car? Could it be Mr. Tang?

09:26.440 --> 09:27.120
I'm back.

09:27.390 --> 09:27.870
Mom.

09:28.200 --> 09:29.460
You're back, Xiaolan?

09:33.910 --> 09:34.550
Granny Yu,

09:35.600 --> 09:36.670
I made some steamed buns.

09:36.670 --> 09:38.270
These are for you. Have a try.

09:42.000 --> 09:43.660
We're heading upstairs then.

10:13.150 --> 10:15.150
Mom, are you just back from Uncle's?

10:15.200 --> 10:16.000
Well, I was helping out

10:16.000 --> 10:17.320
at Mayor Tang's place.

10:19.200 --> 10:19.960
Mayor Tang?

10:20.630 --> 10:21.200
Come on.

10:21.790 --> 10:23.520
Eat the buns while they're hot.

10:25.130 --> 10:27.390
Mayor Tang's stomach problem persists,

10:27.670 --> 10:28.960
and nobody can cook for him at home.

10:28.960 --> 10:30.080
His driver, Wang,

10:30.080 --> 10:31.480
asked if I could help.

10:31.870 --> 10:34.200
So I went
and made him some millet porridge

10:34.320 --> 10:35.360
and steamed buns

10:35.550 --> 10:37.210
that he can have as breakfast.

10:38.220 --> 10:38.820
Actually,

10:38.840 --> 10:40.600
life hasn't been easy for Mayor Tang.

10:40.600 --> 10:42.000
He was divorced long ago.

10:42.360 --> 10:44.760
His children and ex-wife
are now in the U.S.

10:45.200 --> 10:45.910
He has to cook

10:45.910 --> 10:46.750
for himself.

10:47.000 --> 10:49.030
He often skips meals when he gets busy.

10:49.030 --> 10:50.960
That's how he got stomach trouble.

10:52.480 --> 10:53.510
Did you hear all this

10:53.510 --> 10:54.440
from Mayor Tang?

10:54.840 --> 10:56.040
No, Wang told me that.

10:56.510 --> 10:57.510
Mayor wasn't home

10:57.510 --> 10:58.680
when I was cooking there.

10:58.680 --> 10:59.720
I came back as soon as it finished

10:59.720 --> 11:01.050
and didn't wait for him.

11:05.440 --> 11:06.870
Was it appropriate for me to do that?

11:06.870 --> 11:08.400
I did nothing wrong, right?

11:08.960 --> 11:09.630
Right.

11:10.150 --> 11:11.360
You were there to help out.

11:11.360 --> 11:12.820
You got to do as you saw fit.

11:14.910 --> 11:15.440
Mom,

11:16.200 --> 11:17.130
what do you think

11:17.440 --> 11:18.630
of Mayor Tang?

11:20.240 --> 11:22.080
I've only met him a few times.

11:22.740 --> 11:24.270
He seems amicable, though.

11:24.720 --> 11:25.550
Plus...

11:25.730 --> 11:27.060
he's quite polite to me.

11:27.110 --> 11:29.240
Every time, he'd say he owes me thanks.

11:29.840 --> 11:30.550
What else?

11:30.840 --> 11:31.600
Else?

11:32.960 --> 11:34.440
If he were not the mayor,

11:34.720 --> 11:36.250
what would you think of him?

11:37.170 --> 11:38.600
What do you mean,
"if he were not the mayor"?

11:38.600 --> 11:40.060
But he is in fact the mayor.

11:42.840 --> 11:44.370
What are you even thinking?

11:44.870 --> 11:46.030
He's the mayor.

11:46.150 --> 11:47.680
I'm nowhere near his level.

11:48.360 --> 11:49.090
First of all,

11:49.440 --> 11:51.250
I don't think that makes a difference.

11:51.250 --> 11:52.550
It doesn't matter if one is a mayor,
a farm worker,

11:52.550 --> 11:53.630
or a clothing vendor.

11:53.630 --> 11:54.870
Those are just jobs.

11:55.360 --> 11:56.000
Second,

11:56.530 --> 11:57.720
you're both divorced

11:57.720 --> 11:58.440
and single.

11:58.740 --> 11:59.960
I think it's nice for you to get

11:59.960 --> 12:01.420
to know each other better.

12:02.660 --> 12:04.320
You're getting ahead of yourself.

12:04.320 --> 12:05.630
That is impossible.

12:06.000 --> 12:08.080
He's the mayor, a big shot.

12:08.080 --> 12:08.630
I don't even

12:08.630 --> 12:10.490
get to eat at the same table as him.

12:10.870 --> 12:12.270
If, several years ago,

12:12.420 --> 12:13.230
I had told you

12:13.410 --> 12:15.270
you could open clothing stores
in Jingcheng

12:15.270 --> 12:16.200
and Shengcheng,

12:16.480 --> 12:18.410
would you have deemed it possible?

12:19.360 --> 12:20.290
Comrade Liu Fen,

12:20.320 --> 12:20.910
just do

12:20.910 --> 12:22.370
what your heart tells you.

12:22.550 --> 12:25.280
Try not to burden yourself
with so many concerns.

12:28.870 --> 12:29.930
Oh right, Xiaolan,

12:30.030 --> 12:32.080
your uncle said he'd drop by tomorrow

12:32.080 --> 12:32.960
to talk to you

12:32.960 --> 12:34.090
about some project.

12:35.870 --> 12:37.080
It seems it is an opportunity

12:37.080 --> 12:38.610
that comes knocking first.

12:42.670 --> 12:43.270
Cheng.

12:43.720 --> 12:44.870
Still sticking around?

12:44.870 --> 12:45.870
I'm about to finish this.

12:45.870 --> 12:46.480
Hey,

12:46.510 --> 12:47.600
a few days ago, my wife sent me

12:47.600 --> 12:49.000
some local specialties.

12:49.030 --> 12:49.890
They're tasty.

12:49.910 --> 12:50.510
Have a try.

12:51.440 --> 12:51.870
Thanks.

12:51.870 --> 12:52.530
No problem.

12:56.980 --> 12:57.710
It's so sour.

12:57.720 --> 12:58.320
Good, huh?

12:58.720 --> 12:59.390
Keep them then.

12:59.390 --> 13:00.120
I'm leaving.

13:00.320 --> 13:00.630
Thanks.

13:00.630 --> 13:01.630
Don't mention it.

13:05.790 --> 13:06.360
Cheng,

13:06.960 --> 13:07.750
actually,

13:08.000 --> 13:09.630
Mr. Wu just loves to bluff.

13:10.080 --> 13:11.210
Some files, in fact,

13:11.320 --> 13:12.450
aren't that urgent.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.600
Work has to be done sooner or later.

13:15.600 --> 13:18.000
I'd like to finish it early
so I can go back to my girlfriend early.

13:18.000 --> 13:19.660
You two are chummy lovebirds.

13:19.750 --> 13:20.630
When I become a lawyer,

13:20.630 --> 13:21.960
I'll have my wife move here too.

13:21.960 --> 13:22.670
Alright, I'll leave you to it.

13:22.670 --> 13:23.360
I'm taking off.

13:23.360 --> 13:23.670
Take care.

13:23.670 --> 13:24.080
Bye.

13:38.870 --> 13:40.080
My last home improvement client

13:40.080 --> 13:40.880
was a big boss.

13:41.360 --> 13:43.030
He thought I did my job fairly well.

13:43.030 --> 13:43.790
He reckoned me doing

13:43.790 --> 13:44.870
home improvement projects only

13:44.870 --> 13:45.930
was a bit of a waste,

13:46.000 --> 13:48.400
and that I should dabble in
something else.

13:49.090 --> 13:49.880
Xiaolan,

13:49.910 --> 13:52.000
tell me, what is "bidding"?

13:52.550 --> 13:53.550
Simply put,

13:53.550 --> 13:55.240
clients requiring renovation services

13:55.240 --> 13:56.370
tend to shop around.

13:56.720 --> 13:58.030
Bidding means

13:58.030 --> 13:59.200
that as the service provider,

13:59.200 --> 14:00.360
we need to offer samples

14:00.360 --> 14:02.140
for clients to make comparisons.

14:02.140 --> 14:02.960
Is that why you asked me

14:02.960 --> 14:04.390
to take photos of the houses

14:04.390 --> 14:05.790
I renovated previously?

14:05.910 --> 14:06.270
Yes.

14:06.440 --> 14:07.670
You're truly smart, Uncle.

14:07.670 --> 14:09.720
But that's just part of the materials
to be submitted.

14:09.720 --> 14:11.080
Besides the company's credentials

14:11.080 --> 14:12.200
and previous works,

14:12.200 --> 14:14.000
we also need to prepare a tender document

14:14.000 --> 14:15.200
and some design proposals

14:15.200 --> 14:16.800
based on the client's needs.

14:17.120 --> 14:18.270
I can see that this plan

14:18.270 --> 14:19.270
is written in great detail.

14:19.270 --> 14:20.550
It points out
what the tender should include,

14:20.550 --> 14:22.120
so it won't be hard for us to prepare one.

14:22.120 --> 14:23.200
The problem is that we need to

14:23.200 --> 14:24.930
decide which project to bid on.

14:25.030 --> 14:26.360
We have choices on that?

14:26.550 --> 14:27.080
Yes.

14:27.430 --> 14:29.300
This time, the renovation of Shengcheng

14:29.300 --> 14:29.810
Guesthouse

14:29.810 --> 14:31.720
has been split
into several smaller projects.

14:31.720 --> 14:32.630
I guess the purpose is to present

14:32.630 --> 14:34.320
opportunities
to privately owned enterprises.

14:34.320 --> 14:35.630
Otherwise, establishments like Yuanhui,

14:35.630 --> 14:36.390
which used to focus on

14:36.390 --> 14:38.190
home improvement business only

14:38.270 --> 14:40.150
and haven't engaged
in a single government project,

14:40.150 --> 14:41.630
would probably never stand a chance

14:41.630 --> 14:43.290
of participating in this bid.

14:44.030 --> 14:45.390
Then this is an important matter.

14:45.390 --> 14:45.850
Well...

14:46.750 --> 14:48.210
are we able to handle this?

14:48.440 --> 14:49.390
Uncle, don't worry.

14:49.390 --> 14:50.390
I'll be there for you.

14:50.390 --> 14:52.450
Then what about your clothing store?

14:52.510 --> 14:54.320
All is fine. It won't be affected.

14:54.320 --> 14:56.030
Even if we only win
a bid for a tiny project

14:56.030 --> 14:57.120
this time,

14:57.240 --> 14:58.150
we'll still make our way

14:58.150 --> 15:00.410
to the renovation market in Shengcheng.

15:01.410 --> 15:02.720
This seems to be a good opportunity

15:02.720 --> 15:03.790
for Yuanhui.

15:05.030 --> 15:07.270
An opportunity for me, too.

15:08.200 --> 15:08.800
By the way,

15:08.960 --> 15:10.150
two other bidders are

15:10.150 --> 15:10.950
a state-owned

15:11.150 --> 15:11.840
enterprise

15:12.000 --> 15:14.260
and a venture backed by Gangdao capital.

15:14.390 --> 15:16.790
The name of that Gangdao company is...

15:17.200 --> 15:19.600
"Chengrong Tianchen."

15:20.080 --> 15:21.750
You mean Chengrong Group
owned by Du Chengrong

15:21.750 --> 15:22.680
from Gangdao?

15:22.790 --> 15:23.870
Yes, yes,

15:24.000 --> 15:24.530
exactly.

15:32.150 --> 15:33.080
Well, Uncle,

15:34.120 --> 15:35.550
it's about time

15:35.720 --> 15:36.480
I got off work

15:37.000 --> 15:38.000
and went on a date.

15:39.360 --> 15:40.320
I'll get going then.

15:40.320 --> 15:40.840
Bye bye.

15:42.320 --> 15:43.000
Granny Yu,

15:43.240 --> 15:43.750
bye bye.

15:45.630 --> 15:47.600
When young people are in love...

15:48.750 --> 15:49.810
Y-Young people...

15:50.400 --> 15:51.360
I don't live here.

15:51.360 --> 15:52.150
I've rented a place.

15:52.150 --> 15:53.080
I'm leaving now.

16:07.120 --> 16:07.580
Come on.

16:09.120 --> 16:13.720
[Time is money; Efficiency is life]

16:13.150 --> 16:14.200
Wide open views.

16:14.880 --> 16:16.320
Everything's within a glance.

16:16.320 --> 16:17.200
How did you find this place?

16:17.200 --> 16:19.260
I'm Xia Xiaolan. Give me some credit.

16:20.960 --> 16:21.720
Look.

16:22.240 --> 16:24.510
Shengcheng is really huge.

16:25.060 --> 16:26.570
Seeing from your home,

16:26.600 --> 16:27.760
it's a sea of lights.

16:28.400 --> 16:30.000
Seeing from here,

16:30.030 --> 16:32.290
there are bustling commercial streets.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.670
At Shengcheng's pace of development,

16:33.670 --> 16:34.840
it shouldn't be long

16:35.150 --> 16:36.000
before the side across

16:36.000 --> 16:37.600
is filled with skyscrapers.

16:37.960 --> 16:39.440
By then, your real estate agency

16:39.440 --> 16:40.840
can be set up in this area.

16:40.910 --> 16:42.080
Right now, all I want is to

16:42.080 --> 16:43.670
quickly launch my clothing store

16:43.670 --> 16:45.330
and accumulate capital fast.

16:47.520 --> 16:48.450
It would be great

16:48.480 --> 16:50.010
if I could open my shop here.

16:50.150 --> 16:51.480
Surrounded by streets in three sides,

16:51.480 --> 16:52.670
it can be seen

16:52.910 --> 16:54.150
from all intersections.

16:54.150 --> 16:55.840
It will definitely be
the most eye-catching

16:55.840 --> 16:57.770
presence in this entire district.

17:01.720 --> 17:02.320
Look.

17:02.910 --> 17:04.369
That spot with no lights on

17:04.750 --> 17:06.349
probably hasn't been taken yet.

17:06.349 --> 17:07.550
Maybe it's still for rent.

17:07.550 --> 17:08.750
Shall we check it out tomorrow?

17:08.750 --> 17:09.200
Okay.

17:09.349 --> 17:10.000
Right there?

17:10.000 --> 17:11.000
Yes, right there.

17:18.680 --> 17:19.210
Morning.

17:19.400 --> 17:19.720
Morning.

17:19.720 --> 17:20.650
Morning, Cheng.

17:23.829 --> 17:24.890
New environments.

17:25.400 --> 17:26.270
New careers.

17:26.750 --> 17:27.680
New challenges.

17:28.680 --> 17:30.340
We are all trying hard to adapt

17:30.680 --> 17:31.740
and doing our best.

17:34.240 --> 17:35.110
Careful!

17:35.880 --> 17:36.640
Quick.

17:36.920 --> 17:38.200
Work overtime if we have to!

17:38.200 --> 17:38.720
Yes.

17:54.000 --> 17:54.680
Xiaolan,

17:55.790 --> 17:56.720
it's time to eat.

17:56.790 --> 17:57.720
Okay, coming.

18:09.160 --> 18:09.880
Granny Yu,

18:10.070 --> 18:10.920
you're back.

18:11.590 --> 18:13.680
Have you eaten yet? I made dumplings.

18:17.700 --> 18:18.400
Nobody in this world

18:18.400 --> 18:19.810
can be more kind-hearted and nicer

18:19.810 --> 18:21.660
than you, Comrade Liu Fen.

18:32.700 --> 18:35.190
[From Chen Xiliang: Give me a call soon]

18:39.640 --> 18:41.070
You seem to be enjoying this.

18:41.070 --> 18:41.920
Well, any deals

18:41.920 --> 18:43.450
with magazine publishers?

18:45.590 --> 18:46.520
Yes, I nailed it.

18:47.050 --> 18:48.720
For a magazine's issue
for the second half of this month,

18:48.720 --> 18:51.120
the actor Zhou Wangjing
will wear my coats.

18:54.160 --> 18:56.490
Then why are you still
pulling a long face?

18:56.800 --> 18:58.110
I went to great lengths to finally

18:58.110 --> 18:59.570
connect to Zhou Wangjing.

18:59.920 --> 19:00.750
I was being toyed with

19:00.750 --> 19:02.410
by a bunch of magazine editors

19:02.510 --> 19:03.310
all last week.

19:03.640 --> 19:04.680
We'll talk about this later.

19:03.940 --> 19:08.120
[Jingcheng Friend for Fashion Magazine]

19:04.680 --> 19:05.030
Sure.

19:05.070 --> 19:06.270
Shall we have dinner together?

19:06.270 --> 19:06.680
Okay.

19:06.780 --> 19:07.310
Let's go.

19:07.480 --> 19:08.640
Join us then, all of you.

19:08.640 --> 19:09.160
Sure.

19:09.790 --> 19:11.190
Ms. Xia, you have no idea.

19:11.510 --> 19:13.310
Those editors drank lots of wine

19:13.640 --> 19:15.480
and accepted all the presents I gave them.

19:15.480 --> 19:17.160
But when it came to bringing my coats
to the cover,

19:17.160 --> 19:18.030
they started making excuses.

19:18.030 --> 19:18.960
Take it, please.

19:19.680 --> 19:20.410
Here you are.

19:20.520 --> 19:21.350
L-Let me see you out.

19:21.350 --> 19:22.880
No need. Don't stand on ceremony.

19:22.880 --> 19:23.680
Alright then.

19:24.120 --> 19:25.160
Take care, everyone.

19:25.160 --> 19:25.790
Editor-in-Chief.

19:25.790 --> 19:26.270
Okay.

19:26.270 --> 19:26.790
Mr. Chen.

19:26.790 --> 19:27.270
Hey, Mr. Wang.

19:27.270 --> 19:27.830
Just wait to hear from us.

19:27.830 --> 19:28.550
Take care.

19:28.680 --> 19:29.680
Thank you so much!

19:29.680 --> 19:30.110
No problem.

19:30.110 --> 19:31.070
Come visit Shengcheng when available!

19:31.070 --> 19:31.830
Sure, sure.

19:34.030 --> 19:35.440
Later, enlightened by a kind soul,

19:35.440 --> 19:36.640
I realized the truth.

19:37.040 --> 19:38.590
Those editors looked down on me for being

19:38.590 --> 19:39.790
a self-employed stall vendor.

19:39.790 --> 19:40.720
Though I offered to sponsor them

19:40.720 --> 19:42.350
with free apparel
for the magazine's photoshoots,

19:42.350 --> 19:44.480
they still turned their noses up at it.

19:45.830 --> 19:46.640
Have you eaten yet?

19:46.640 --> 19:47.550
Care for some noodles?

19:47.550 --> 19:48.680
No need. I've eaten.

19:48.790 --> 19:49.450
Herbal tea?

19:49.920 --> 19:50.400
Okay.

19:51.000 --> 19:51.400
Sir,

19:51.550 --> 19:52.260
two cups of herbal tea.

19:52.260 --> 19:53.190
Okay, just a sec.

19:54.070 --> 19:54.680
Ms. Xia,

19:55.350 --> 19:56.460
don't you think those

19:56.460 --> 19:58.320
men's coats I designed look nice?

19:58.750 --> 20:00.280
Aren't the fabric and style

20:00.400 --> 20:01.440
high-class enough?

20:01.440 --> 20:02.790
I think they're perfect.

20:02.790 --> 20:03.590
The editors rejected me

20:03.590 --> 20:05.400
because I don't own a brand, right?

20:05.400 --> 20:06.680
That aside,

20:07.030 --> 20:08.560
what else do I fall short of?

20:09.510 --> 20:10.640
As you just said,

20:10.960 --> 20:12.720
the only thing you lack is a brand.

20:12.720 --> 20:13.350
If you have

20:13.370 --> 20:14.440
your own brand

20:14.550 --> 20:16.440
and hire actors to shoot commercials

20:16.440 --> 20:18.240
for the clothes designed by you—

20:18.350 --> 20:19.680
like the ones on TV,

20:19.920 --> 20:20.720
you won't have to beg...

20:20.720 --> 20:21.830
Have my own brand?

20:25.160 --> 20:27.420
I've been thinking about the same thing.

20:28.590 --> 20:29.310
Ms. Xia,

20:29.680 --> 20:30.740
respected Ms. Xia,

20:30.830 --> 20:31.960
I knew the two of us

20:31.960 --> 20:33.760
would come up with the same idea.

20:34.750 --> 20:36.010
Again, I said too much.

20:36.240 --> 20:37.510
Actually, on my way here,

20:37.510 --> 20:39.200
I was contemplating it the entire time.

20:39.200 --> 20:40.240
I think the two of us

20:40.240 --> 20:42.100
can partner up and create a brand.

20:42.510 --> 20:43.270
We can hire actors

20:43.270 --> 20:44.740
to shoot commercials like you said.

20:44.740 --> 20:45.870
I believe, that way,

20:45.880 --> 20:47.610
we can make a name for our brand.

20:48.200 --> 20:50.060
In the timeline where I came from,

20:50.440 --> 20:52.960
it'd take Chen Xiliang a few more years

20:53.250 --> 20:54.200
to officially launch

20:54.200 --> 20:55.960
"Luna," the brand that brought him wealth.

20:55.960 --> 20:57.920
Now, it's going to happen ahead of time.

20:57.920 --> 20:58.480
I'm not sure

20:58.480 --> 21:00.030
what changes this will trigger.

21:00.030 --> 21:00.680
Ms. Xia.

21:01.160 --> 21:02.160
Dear Ms. Xia.

21:02.880 --> 21:03.960
My dearest Ms. Xia,

21:04.640 --> 21:06.370
please do give it some thought.

21:06.880 --> 21:08.410
Let's partner up, shall we?

21:10.310 --> 21:12.490
Perhaps this is a foreshadowing of fate.

21:12.490 --> 21:13.110
I don't know

21:13.110 --> 21:15.070
what kind of story that my encounter

21:15.070 --> 21:16.730
with Chen Xiliang will begin.

21:18.200 --> 21:19.270
Dear Ms. Xia,

21:19.680 --> 21:21.540
I'm not suggesting it on impulse.

21:21.640 --> 21:24.000
I have to earn my money hard
from wholesale.

21:24.000 --> 21:25.440
I'm not content with that.

21:25.440 --> 21:27.000
People would sneeze at me if I offered

21:27.000 --> 21:28.240
to alter their garments.

21:28.240 --> 21:29.550
I also think that's beneath me.

21:29.550 --> 21:31.030
Creating a brand is a path

21:31.030 --> 21:31.920
taken by few.

21:32.400 --> 21:33.510
Others don't have the guts,

21:33.510 --> 21:34.200
but I do.

21:34.680 --> 21:35.540
I'd like to try.

21:36.920 --> 21:37.640
It is indeed

21:37.640 --> 21:39.240
a good idea to create a brand.

21:39.440 --> 21:40.590
That said, you're an expert

21:40.590 --> 21:41.680
at tailoring and designs,

21:41.680 --> 21:43.750
and your family has connections
with garment factories.

21:43.750 --> 21:45.210
Why partner with me at all?

21:45.400 --> 21:47.310
Because you have a knack for sales.

21:47.310 --> 21:48.160
I understand.

21:48.750 --> 21:50.280
Nice clothes are just rags

21:50.310 --> 21:51.370
if they can't sell.

21:51.860 --> 21:53.830
I couldn't have fathomed
what you thought of—

21:53.830 --> 21:55.030
an ad campaign through a magazine.

21:55.030 --> 21:56.160
You have what I need.

22:05.000 --> 22:05.550
Although

22:06.110 --> 22:07.750
we've only met a few times,

22:08.150 --> 22:09.280
I can feel...

22:09.310 --> 22:11.270
that you're different from everyone else.

22:11.270 --> 22:12.510
It's just like...

22:13.960 --> 22:14.640
like...

22:15.550 --> 22:17.950
you popped up from nowhere
to come to my aid.

22:18.070 --> 22:20.070
You're like a gift from heaven to me.

22:21.270 --> 22:22.960
As long as you agree to work with me,

22:22.960 --> 22:24.160
I'll say yes to any...

22:26.550 --> 22:29.550
I mean, I'll really consider
any conditions you make.

22:30.270 --> 22:31.110
I know

22:31.400 --> 22:32.750
there have to be certain rules

22:32.750 --> 22:34.680
when we become business partners.

22:35.380 --> 22:36.270
But don't you worry.

22:36.270 --> 22:38.930
I'll definitely not
put you in a difficult spot.

22:39.750 --> 22:40.480
Mr. Chen,

22:41.030 --> 22:42.230
if you had just said

22:42.260 --> 22:43.640
you'd say yes to any conditions I made,

22:43.640 --> 22:45.840
I would've stood up and left right away.

22:46.110 --> 22:48.510
I bit my tongue at the last moment,
didn't I?

22:49.110 --> 22:51.590
Right now, I do need

22:51.590 --> 22:52.920
a profitable business.

22:53.920 --> 22:55.180
You and your brand have

22:55.640 --> 22:57.100
great potential, indeed.

22:57.780 --> 22:58.920
When it comes to garment making,

22:58.920 --> 23:01.120
you truly have more resources than I do.

23:01.400 --> 23:02.550
I can handle marketing,

23:02.550 --> 23:03.480
but you'll have to run

23:03.480 --> 23:05.610
the day-to-day operations yourself.

23:08.160 --> 23:09.020
How about this?

23:09.720 --> 23:12.160
I'll take 45% of the shares,

23:12.480 --> 23:13.310
and you 55%.

23:14.030 --> 23:15.000
What do you think?

23:15.000 --> 23:15.550
I agree.

23:16.230 --> 23:16.790
Look,

23:17.030 --> 23:19.160
I'll draft a contract as soon as possible.

23:19.160 --> 23:19.880
We can discuss

23:19.880 --> 23:20.940
the details later.

23:21.200 --> 23:23.040
Your boyfriend Zhou is a paralegal.

23:23.040 --> 23:24.110
I will definitely not

23:24.110 --> 23:25.070
play any tricks in the contract.

23:25.070 --> 23:26.670
You can rest assured of that.

23:27.030 --> 23:28.240
Let's make it a great cause,

23:28.240 --> 23:29.970
now that we're committed to it.

23:30.350 --> 23:31.830
Our current goal is to open branches

23:31.830 --> 23:33.270
in all major cities across the country

23:33.270 --> 23:34.400
within one year.

23:35.070 --> 23:37.530
Where would you like
to place our first shop?

23:37.890 --> 23:39.710
I can get hold of many resources
in Longcheng,

23:39.710 --> 23:40.640
and I'm familiar with that city.

23:40.640 --> 23:42.270
It won't be hard to open a shop there.

23:42.270 --> 23:44.670
Given Shengcheng's proximity to Gangdao,

23:45.240 --> 23:47.370
I think we should have a shop there too.

23:47.880 --> 23:49.400
We're opening shops anyway. How about

23:49.400 --> 23:50.660
we open two at one time?

23:53.550 --> 23:54.610
One in Shengcheng.

23:54.750 --> 23:55.750
Two in Longcheng.

23:55.880 --> 23:56.830
What do you think?

23:56.830 --> 23:58.350
We'll open three shops on the same day

23:58.350 --> 23:59.480
to make a big splash.

23:59.680 --> 24:00.380
Sounds good.

24:00.380 --> 24:02.310
Let's open three shops all at once.

24:02.640 --> 24:04.240
I've been to Gangdao before.

24:04.510 --> 24:06.310
The shops there all use English.

24:06.510 --> 24:08.240
They look fancy and stylish

24:08.440 --> 24:09.070
to me.

24:09.440 --> 24:10.720
You've been to college.

24:10.720 --> 24:11.980
I'm sure you know a lot.

24:12.270 --> 24:14.160
Why don't you give a name to our brand?

24:14.160 --> 24:15.200
No, this is your own brand.

24:15.200 --> 24:16.800
You should name it yourself.

24:16.920 --> 24:18.450
I can offer you some advice.

24:19.240 --> 24:20.070
I'll buy an English dictionary

24:20.070 --> 24:22.000
and flip through it for ideas then.

24:22.570 --> 24:24.420
As for the shop in Shengcheng,

24:24.590 --> 24:25.480
I'll have to trouble you

24:25.480 --> 24:26.940
to help me pick a location.

24:27.750 --> 24:28.920
Shengcheng...

24:30.030 --> 24:31.690
There's actually a nice spot.

24:35.790 --> 24:36.520
Ms. Xia,

24:37.000 --> 24:38.680
you really are my lifesaver.

24:38.920 --> 24:40.450
What a wonderful location.

24:40.450 --> 24:41.550
Whichever way people come from,

24:41.550 --> 24:43.080
they'll see our shop first.

24:47.270 --> 24:48.250
Wait, something's off.

24:48.250 --> 24:48.970
Why hasn't

24:49.000 --> 24:50.960
this prime location been rented yet?

24:50.960 --> 24:52.760
I've inquired about this place.

24:53.240 --> 24:54.510
The ground floor is for shops,

24:54.510 --> 24:56.070
and the second for apartments.

24:56.070 --> 24:58.110
This property
partly belongs to a food factory,

24:58.110 --> 24:58.680
and partly

24:58.680 --> 24:59.680
to an individual.

24:59.920 --> 25:02.310
That person is said to be
very difficult to deal with.

25:02.310 --> 25:04.030
So the food factory would rather

25:04.030 --> 25:05.200
leave this building vacant

25:05.200 --> 25:06.240
than bother to hold

25:06.240 --> 25:07.100
a negotiation.

25:07.310 --> 25:08.310
What a hassle.

25:10.110 --> 25:12.310
Success requires addressing trouble.

25:12.920 --> 25:13.800
Just go back to Longcheng

25:13.800 --> 25:15.400
and get the brand and trademark ready.

25:15.400 --> 25:17.070
However hard it is to strike a lease deal,

25:17.070 --> 25:18.640
I'll make sure we secure this spot.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.200
Okay.

25:22.980 --> 25:23.740
Granny Yu,

25:24.430 --> 25:26.440
I just learned how to make
stir-fried rice noodles with beef.

25:26.440 --> 25:27.420
I heard people here

25:27.420 --> 25:28.310
all enjoy this.

25:28.510 --> 25:30.440
Taste it and tell me what you think.

25:33.310 --> 25:33.830
Mom,

25:34.270 --> 25:36.530
that old lady hasn't warmed up to you yet?

25:37.310 --> 25:38.370
It won't take long.

25:41.830 --> 25:42.540
Let me help.

25:42.720 --> 25:44.000
Mind the stuff. Close the door.

25:44.000 --> 25:44.270
Got it.

25:44.270 --> 25:45.010
Yong...

25:49.030 --> 25:51.070
Where did you get these many paintings?

25:51.070 --> 25:52.000
Xiaolan asked me

25:52.110 --> 25:53.820
to get her some oil paintings.

25:53.960 --> 25:54.920
Tell me where you want them to be,

25:54.920 --> 25:55.960
and I'll hang them up later.

25:55.960 --> 25:57.220
Okay. Let's eat first.

25:59.070 --> 26:00.440
Stir-fried rice noodles with beef?

26:00.440 --> 26:00.970
Try some.

26:01.080 --> 26:01.830
Though I've been here

26:01.830 --> 26:02.720
for many years,

26:03.010 --> 26:03.930
I still think

26:03.960 --> 26:05.590
the braised noodles in our hometown
are the best.

26:05.590 --> 26:06.790
I'm not used to this stuff.

26:06.790 --> 26:08.000
Xiaolan, you try some.

26:08.000 --> 26:08.640
I'll taste it then.

26:08.640 --> 26:10.570
Did I not make it the authentic way?

26:12.180 --> 26:13.710
You already did a great job.

26:14.270 --> 26:15.160
But people's taste in food

26:15.160 --> 26:16.490
doesn't change easily.

26:16.650 --> 26:17.280
I guess

26:17.310 --> 26:19.310
it'll taste better with some chili.

26:19.720 --> 26:20.780
Oh right, Xiaolan.

26:21.110 --> 26:22.970
I asked about that small building

26:23.030 --> 26:24.160
you have your eye on.

26:24.240 --> 26:25.400
The food factory finds it

26:25.400 --> 26:26.110
too troublesome

26:26.110 --> 26:27.370
to hold a negotiation.

26:27.880 --> 26:28.920
Can they give us

26:28.920 --> 26:30.290
the other owner's information

26:30.290 --> 26:30.900
then?

26:31.160 --> 26:32.320
We'll talk to this person ourselves.

26:32.320 --> 26:33.440
When the three parties reach an agreement,

26:33.440 --> 26:35.540
all we will need to do is sit down
and sign a contract.

26:35.540 --> 26:36.340
Oh right, Mom.

26:36.800 --> 26:38.240
When the Shengcheng shop opens,

26:38.240 --> 26:39.510
you'll be the manager of it.

26:39.510 --> 26:41.080
Chen Xiliang has agreed to that.

26:41.080 --> 26:42.310
Well, Uncle, about that building,

26:42.310 --> 26:43.310
I'm afraid I'll have to trouble you

26:43.310 --> 26:44.110
to make inquiries again.

26:44.110 --> 26:44.510
No problem.

26:44.510 --> 26:45.440
I'm already scheduled to meet with someone

26:45.440 --> 26:46.240
and talk about it this afternoon.

26:46.240 --> 26:46.590
Okay.

26:46.790 --> 26:47.640
Tell me where you'd like

26:47.640 --> 26:48.510
to place these oil paintings.

26:48.510 --> 26:50.400
I'll hang them up for you after lunch.

26:50.400 --> 26:51.080
No need for that.

26:51.080 --> 26:52.800
The paintings are for bidding

26:52.830 --> 26:54.360
on the guesthouse project.

26:54.680 --> 26:55.270
Xiaolan,

26:56.050 --> 26:57.350
are you giving them away as gifts?

26:57.350 --> 26:58.400
Isn't it inappropriate?

26:58.400 --> 26:59.400
Don't get me wrong.

26:59.400 --> 27:01.730
We'll compete based on our capabilities.

27:01.750 --> 27:03.240
But we need to show our advantages

27:03.240 --> 27:04.770
during the bidding, right?

27:05.680 --> 27:06.940
Let me check these out.

27:20.440 --> 27:20.970
Alright.

27:21.680 --> 27:22.400
This is the one.

27:22.150 --> 27:24.120
[Gong Yang, Art Academy]

27:30.400 --> 27:31.000
Xiaolan.

27:31.400 --> 27:32.920
I look smart in this, don't I?

27:32.920 --> 27:33.720
My little bag.

27:34.400 --> 27:35.590
Let me tuck it under my arm.

27:35.590 --> 27:36.520
Perfect, right?

27:36.720 --> 27:37.120
Right.

27:37.270 --> 27:39.870
You do look the part
of a private entrepreneur.

27:41.680 --> 27:43.340
That must be Gong Yang, right?

27:45.680 --> 27:46.280
Gong Yang!

27:47.660 --> 27:48.990
Hello, I'm Xia Xiaolan.

27:51.400 --> 27:53.200
This is Mr. Liu, the owner of Yuanhui.

27:53.200 --> 27:54.260
He's also my uncle.

27:54.450 --> 27:55.270
Today, you'll be with us

27:55.270 --> 27:56.160
for a tour first.

27:56.160 --> 27:57.240
Then I'll tell you

27:57.240 --> 27:58.640
our specific requirements.

27:58.640 --> 27:59.070
Okay.

27:59.550 --> 28:00.640
I have classes this afternoon.

28:00.640 --> 28:02.170
How long will the tour take?

28:02.240 --> 28:02.970
Don't worry.

28:03.030 --> 28:05.290
We promise you won't be late for classes.

28:06.110 --> 28:07.400
If it isn't Xia Xiaolan,

28:07.400 --> 28:08.350
Ms. Xia.

28:10.070 --> 28:11.510
Long time no see, Ms. Xia.

28:12.200 --> 28:14.110
It turns out you're pursuing a career

28:14.110 --> 28:15.320
in the renovation industry.

28:15.320 --> 28:17.520
But I think a talented lady like you,

28:17.550 --> 28:18.480
Ms. Xia,

28:18.790 --> 28:20.070
should join a big corporation,

28:20.070 --> 28:22.270
a design institute, or something alike,

28:22.270 --> 28:23.690
even if you're not going to Gangdao.

28:23.690 --> 28:24.920
Why did you choose this company,

28:24.920 --> 28:26.440
which seems to be struggling?

28:26.440 --> 28:27.240
I wonder, Ms. Xia,

28:27.240 --> 28:28.440
if you have heard of a company

28:28.440 --> 28:29.970
named Chengrong Tianchen.

28:30.110 --> 28:32.030
It invests generously in every project.

28:32.030 --> 28:32.880
You're exactly

28:32.880 --> 28:34.880
the kind of talent we need right now.

28:35.760 --> 28:36.650
Mr. Du,

28:37.240 --> 28:39.880
since this "struggling company" of ours

28:40.030 --> 28:41.590
can be a rival to that "generous company"

28:41.590 --> 28:42.400
of yours,

28:42.640 --> 28:43.240
it means

28:43.240 --> 28:44.970
ours has boundless prospects.

28:45.310 --> 28:46.720
I prefer to stay

28:47.070 --> 28:48.400
where there is a future.

28:50.510 --> 28:51.240
Fair enough.

28:51.730 --> 28:53.410
If we can

28:53.440 --> 28:54.830
cooperate this time,

28:55.420 --> 28:56.920
I'd love to have more exchanges

28:56.920 --> 28:58.000
with you, Ms. Xia.

28:58.960 --> 29:00.270
I don't think your mind

29:00.270 --> 29:01.880
is on the bidding at all, Mr. Du.

29:01.880 --> 29:03.470
You and I have nothing to talk about.

29:03.470 --> 29:04.400
Let's go, Uncle.

29:08.030 --> 29:08.690
Sassy girl.

29:10.240 --> 29:11.170
The guesthouse

29:11.200 --> 29:13.110
has 67 rooms of various sizes,

29:13.480 --> 29:14.940
3 large conference rooms,

29:15.000 --> 29:16.400
and 9 smaller ones.

29:16.830 --> 29:18.290
There are 2 dinning halls,

29:18.350 --> 29:19.920
and one reception lobby.

29:20.380 --> 29:21.050
These places all

29:21.050 --> 29:23.070
fall within the scope of this tender.

29:23.070 --> 29:24.550
You can bid for renovating them all,

29:24.550 --> 29:26.520
or just some of them.

29:26.930 --> 29:27.440
You can find

29:27.440 --> 29:28.610
all this information in our profile.

29:28.610 --> 29:29.350
Please refer to it

29:29.350 --> 29:30.640
for more details.

29:31.480 --> 29:33.160
Also, you can take on-site measurements

29:33.160 --> 29:34.440
if necessary.

29:34.750 --> 29:36.150
Can we take a look around?

29:36.310 --> 29:36.830
Sure.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.130
I'll be in my office.

29:38.130 --> 29:39.510
Let me know if you need anything.

29:39.510 --> 29:39.920
Okay.

29:39.940 --> 29:40.940
Got it, thank you.

29:40.960 --> 29:41.590
Thanks!

29:42.240 --> 29:43.400
Uncle, shall we check out

29:43.400 --> 29:44.240
the dining halls downstairs?

29:44.240 --> 29:45.100
Sure, let's go.

29:48.720 --> 29:49.270
Mr. Du.

29:50.000 --> 29:50.480
Ms. Xia,

29:50.550 --> 29:51.640
what can I do for you?

29:51.640 --> 29:53.570
We are competitors now, aren't we?

29:53.750 --> 29:55.070
Why are you following me?

29:55.070 --> 29:56.800
Aren't your people over there?

29:56.920 --> 29:58.000
Good thing that we're competitors.

29:58.000 --> 29:59.000
We can cooperate.

29:59.920 --> 30:01.030
Cooperate with a seemingly

30:01.030 --> 30:02.890
"struggling company" like ours?

30:03.550 --> 30:04.590
Of course.

30:11.590 --> 30:12.130
Xiaolan,

30:12.160 --> 30:13.000
look at this place.

30:13.000 --> 30:13.750
How very nice.

30:13.750 --> 30:15.080
Such a huge dining hall.

30:16.440 --> 30:16.880
By the way,

30:16.880 --> 30:17.750
you seem to be acquainted

30:17.750 --> 30:19.240
with that rich young fella.

30:19.240 --> 30:20.440
I met him in Jingcheng.

30:20.440 --> 30:21.900
He is Xia Dajun's boss now.

30:22.720 --> 30:23.480
Xia Dajun?

30:24.240 --> 30:25.700
How is Xia Dajun involved?

30:26.160 --> 30:26.830
I've explained everything

30:26.830 --> 30:28.190
about Xia Dajun to that rich guy.

30:28.190 --> 30:30.080
Now, he's just trying to chase after me.

30:30.080 --> 30:30.920
I guess he deliberately

30:30.920 --> 30:32.250
followed us here today.

30:32.790 --> 30:33.800
That explains it.

30:34.070 --> 30:34.920
All the other companies

30:34.920 --> 30:35.740
pay visits separately,

30:35.740 --> 30:37.670
yet he insists on sticking with us.

30:37.970 --> 30:39.030
I've asked around.

30:39.170 --> 30:40.440
His colleague
who's in charge of the bidding—

30:40.440 --> 30:41.720
you remember that bald guy?

30:41.720 --> 30:42.640
He's responsible for the part.

30:42.640 --> 30:43.590
But actually, he hasn't

30:43.590 --> 30:44.510
made anything great.

30:44.510 --> 30:45.200
He's just riding

30:45.200 --> 30:46.240
on Chengrong Tianchen's

30:46.240 --> 30:47.270
coattails.

30:48.920 --> 30:50.110
Okay. Let's just be ourselves

30:50.110 --> 30:50.750
and ignore the others.

30:50.750 --> 30:51.310
That's right.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.170
Uncle, you see,

30:52.680 --> 30:54.960
today, the most lucrative part
of the project is actually

30:54.960 --> 30:55.890
the guest rooms.

30:55.960 --> 30:58.050
But renovating all of them
will take a long time,

30:58.050 --> 30:58.880
and we're in no position

30:58.880 --> 30:59.720
to front that much money.

30:59.720 --> 31:00.240
Yeah.

31:00.680 --> 31:02.240
Sixty-seven rooms.

31:02.240 --> 31:03.110
My goodness.

31:03.350 --> 31:04.440
So tempting.

31:05.480 --> 31:06.280
What a shame.

31:06.310 --> 31:06.810
It's okay.

31:06.810 --> 31:08.880
Other opportunities are open to us, right?

31:08.880 --> 31:10.440
Three large conference rooms

31:10.440 --> 31:11.790
and nine less big.

31:11.930 --> 31:12.840
Since it's a smaller bid,

31:12.840 --> 31:14.030
it should be easier to win.

31:14.030 --> 31:15.440
The same goes for the dining halls.

31:15.440 --> 31:16.680
Uncle, which do you prefer?

31:16.680 --> 31:17.830
Wait. I don't understand.

31:17.830 --> 31:18.960
If the dining halls,

31:19.030 --> 31:20.090
conference rooms,

31:20.100 --> 31:20.960
and guest rooms

31:21.250 --> 31:22.550
are renovated by different contractors,

31:22.550 --> 31:24.700
w-won't they be of inconsistent styles?

31:24.700 --> 31:25.800
Then let's come up with

31:25.800 --> 31:27.900
a design plan featuring a unified style.

31:27.900 --> 31:29.400
Consider it our way to help the guesthouse

31:29.400 --> 31:30.070
solve a problem.

31:30.070 --> 31:30.920
But why should we?

31:30.920 --> 31:31.680
If we not only draw

31:31.680 --> 31:32.640
designs for our own target,

31:32.640 --> 31:33.440
and but also for others',

31:33.440 --> 31:34.640
won't that be a loss for us?

31:34.640 --> 31:35.590
Don't worry about that.

31:35.590 --> 31:36.920
I've planned it all out.

31:37.750 --> 31:38.550
That young man Gong Yang

31:38.550 --> 31:39.950
is hired by me to help out.

31:40.160 --> 31:41.400
Gong Yang, what do you think?

31:41.400 --> 31:42.730
Are you interested now?

31:46.540 --> 31:48.270
Hotels and guesthouses

31:48.340 --> 31:49.710
have the same focus:

31:49.740 --> 31:50.960
a coherent overall style.

31:50.960 --> 31:52.790
It seems we're adding a bit more
to our workload

31:52.790 --> 31:54.520
by producing a comprehensive scheme,

31:54.520 --> 31:55.350
but that extra bit

31:55.350 --> 31:56.270
will give us

31:56.490 --> 31:57.310
a big enough edge

31:57.310 --> 31:58.770
to crush our competitors.

31:59.240 --> 32:01.450
Yuanhui is young and not very competive.

32:01.450 --> 32:02.830
But if our comprehensive proposal

32:02.830 --> 32:03.630
is good enough

32:03.790 --> 32:04.680
to be adopted,

32:05.040 --> 32:06.440
won't we at least get a little share
of the profits,

32:06.440 --> 32:08.970
though the major part
will be taken by others?

32:12.010 --> 32:16.460
[Shengcheng Guesthouse]

32:14.000 --> 32:14.600
Gong Yang.

32:14.920 --> 32:16.640
I know your major is oil painting,

32:16.640 --> 32:17.960
and you crave a career in the fine arts.

32:17.960 --> 32:19.750
But since your family is of modest means,

32:19.750 --> 32:21.640
you want to make money from this job.

32:21.640 --> 32:22.480
Ms. Xia, I...

32:22.510 --> 32:24.000
Making money is a very reasonable

32:24.000 --> 32:25.310
and legitimate desire.

32:25.310 --> 32:26.750
Don't feel embarrassed about it.

32:26.750 --> 32:28.750
Small though our company is,

32:28.880 --> 32:30.400
we highly value talent.

32:30.790 --> 32:32.030
We won't treat you as cheap labor

32:32.030 --> 32:33.760
just because you're a student.

32:34.160 --> 32:35.780
As long as you draw the design renderings

32:35.780 --> 32:36.940
as per my instructions,

32:36.940 --> 32:37.880
I'll be happy to pay you

32:37.880 --> 32:39.350
as much as an assistant designer

32:39.350 --> 32:40.200
deserves.

32:41.440 --> 32:42.240
I used to only do

32:42.240 --> 32:43.440
paintings at school.

32:43.570 --> 32:44.570
To be honest,

32:44.760 --> 32:45.720
I don't fully undertand

32:45.720 --> 32:46.780
what you just said.

32:46.960 --> 32:48.010
But when I heard your idea

32:48.010 --> 32:49.310
of winning a bid by offering a free

32:49.310 --> 32:50.510
comprehensive proposal,

32:50.510 --> 32:51.400
I found you utterly different

32:51.400 --> 32:52.130
from others.

32:53.240 --> 32:54.040
I've decided.

32:54.550 --> 32:55.680
I'd like to work for you

32:55.680 --> 32:56.740
and learn from you.

32:57.200 --> 32:58.330
I'm just not sure if I can

32:58.330 --> 32:59.730
meet your requirements.

33:00.350 --> 33:01.410
Don't fret so soon.

33:01.440 --> 33:02.590
I'll go over the specifics with you

33:02.590 --> 33:03.770
when there's a general plan.

33:03.770 --> 33:05.720
You don't need to prepare in advance,

33:05.720 --> 33:07.270
because what I want...

33:08.000 --> 33:09.730
might not exist in this era yet.

33:14.830 --> 33:15.400
Xiaolan,

33:15.640 --> 33:16.200
let's go.

33:16.590 --> 33:17.110
Okay.

33:21.880 --> 33:23.810
Do you have to come this close to me?

33:24.030 --> 33:24.550
What?

33:24.550 --> 33:26.110
Do you even know how to drive?

33:26.110 --> 33:27.030
-What are you saying?
-Hua.

33:27.030 --> 33:28.110
You pulled up too close. I...

33:28.110 --> 33:28.830
Hua!

33:30.000 --> 33:30.550
Didn't you hear him

33:30.550 --> 33:31.590
asking if you know how to drive?

33:31.590 --> 33:32.510
Be careful.

33:32.510 --> 33:33.920
Fine, I got it.

33:37.720 --> 33:38.400
Ms. Xia,

33:39.310 --> 33:40.720
I wonder if I have the honor

33:40.720 --> 33:41.980
to treat you to coffee.

33:42.440 --> 33:42.960
Sorry.

33:43.160 --> 33:44.400
I already have plans with my boyfriend.

33:44.400 --> 33:44.930
Let's go.

33:46.480 --> 33:47.200
Take care!

33:49.200 --> 33:49.830
Bye bye.

33:50.550 --> 33:51.510
See you later.

33:55.240 --> 33:55.840
Take care.

33:55.920 --> 33:56.550
Goodbye!

33:57.350 --> 33:58.550
That young beauty...

33:59.000 --> 34:00.260
is quite interesting.

34:02.440 --> 34:03.000
Mr. Du,

34:03.270 --> 34:05.110
this guesthouse project
is no big deal at all.

34:05.110 --> 34:06.910
We can take it all effortlessly.

34:07.310 --> 34:08.710
Since it's a piece of cake,

34:08.710 --> 34:10.710
what's the point in fighting for it?

34:11.230 --> 34:11.760
No...

34:16.710 --> 34:18.400
What? You don't get it?

34:19.480 --> 34:20.110
Why not

34:20.880 --> 34:22.480
just let Xia Xiaolan have it?

34:35.710 --> 34:38.510
Mr. Du basically told us
to cut that girl some slack.

34:38.510 --> 34:40.670
He changes girlfriends three times a week.

34:40.670 --> 34:42.550
He wants me to do a favor for him now?

34:42.550 --> 34:43.440
Not a chance.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.159
Go get the car.

34:45.920 --> 34:54.360
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

34:53.110 --> 34:55.150
You're Xiaolan, Cheng's girlfriend, right?

34:55.150 --> 34:55.810
Yes. Hello.

34:55.840 --> 34:56.280
Hello.

34:56.510 --> 34:57.910
How did you get to know me?

34:58.110 --> 34:58.800
Everyone

34:58.800 --> 35:00.400
in this law firm knows about you.

35:00.400 --> 35:02.530
You look even better than in the photo.

35:02.840 --> 35:03.440
Thank you.

35:03.670 --> 35:04.440
You're welcome.

35:04.440 --> 35:05.480
Well, just go ahead.

35:05.480 --> 35:06.070
No one else is in there,

35:06.070 --> 35:06.760
except Cheng.

35:06.760 --> 35:07.360
I'm leaving now.

35:07.360 --> 35:08.230
Okay. Thank you.

35:08.230 --> 35:08.890
No problem.

35:22.480 --> 35:23.140
Zhou Cheng!

35:24.920 --> 35:25.630
There you are.

35:25.630 --> 35:26.290
Have dinner

35:26.400 --> 35:27.330
before you work.

35:27.440 --> 35:28.900
Or your stomach will hurt.

35:29.150 --> 35:29.590
Okay.

35:30.070 --> 35:30.670
Come here.

35:32.110 --> 35:32.640
Sit down.

35:34.760 --> 35:35.280
Sure.

35:36.320 --> 35:38.380
What delicious food did you bring me?

35:41.800 --> 35:43.510
Why did you put my photo here?

35:44.880 --> 35:46.110
When I first started working in this firm,

35:46.110 --> 35:47.550
an older lady in the logistics department

35:47.550 --> 35:49.160
relentlessly tried to
set me up with girls.

35:49.160 --> 35:50.800
She introduced to me every single girl

35:50.800 --> 35:52.660
she's related to or friends with.

35:54.150 --> 35:55.130
That makes sense.

35:55.130 --> 35:56.280
After all, who doesn't want to

35:56.280 --> 35:57.510
bring home such a handsome

35:57.510 --> 35:59.310
and capable boyfriend like you?

36:00.440 --> 36:01.480
I told that lady

36:01.590 --> 36:02.760
that I already have a girlfriend.

36:02.760 --> 36:04.230
At first, she didn't believe it.

36:04.230 --> 36:05.280
Later on, she said

36:05.960 --> 36:07.770
it wouldn't matter
as I wasn't married yet.

36:07.770 --> 36:09.190
It wasn't until I put this photo out

36:09.190 --> 36:10.520
did she finally give up.

36:12.190 --> 36:13.550
Why?

36:14.480 --> 36:15.550
That's because

36:16.110 --> 36:17.030
my girlfriend

36:17.510 --> 36:19.710
is such a beautiful and excellent lady.

36:20.920 --> 36:21.840
She then even got worried that I might

36:21.840 --> 36:22.630
not be good enough for you.

36:22.630 --> 36:23.320
So she's been

36:23.320 --> 36:24.980
teaching me how to please you.

36:26.380 --> 36:27.910
Are all the other employees

36:28.030 --> 36:29.160
of the firm away now?

36:31.710 --> 36:33.000
Small though this firm is,

36:33.000 --> 36:34.120
it takes on many cases.

36:34.120 --> 36:34.840
Everyone has

36:34.840 --> 36:35.770
several on hand.

36:37.480 --> 36:38.340
What about you?

36:40.880 --> 36:42.140
I'm new here, aren't I?

36:42.550 --> 36:44.400
I'm doing paperwork for now
and getting familiar

36:44.400 --> 36:45.660
with everything here.

36:46.820 --> 36:48.780
Look, these are of the same style.

36:48.810 --> 36:50.030
They can be put together.

36:50.030 --> 36:51.830
And these are of similar colors,

36:52.150 --> 36:53.190
so keep them apart.

36:53.190 --> 36:55.230
This way,
it's easier for customers to distinguish.

36:55.230 --> 36:55.920
Attention to detail

36:55.920 --> 36:57.370
is a must for street vendors then.

36:57.370 --> 36:57.970
Of course.

36:58.000 --> 36:59.920
There's a lot more for you to learn.

36:59.920 --> 37:00.510
Hey,

37:01.070 --> 37:01.960
I bought this yesterday.

37:01.960 --> 37:02.510
But I don't want it now.

37:02.510 --> 37:03.550
I'd like to return it.

37:03.550 --> 37:04.230
Return it?

37:04.710 --> 37:05.710
Let me see.

37:06.000 --> 37:07.510
Will you let me return it or not?

37:07.510 --> 37:09.400
Look, all sales are final.

37:09.400 --> 37:10.880
Don't I need to check the item
before it's returned?

37:10.880 --> 37:11.740
This is a refusal, isn't it?

37:11.740 --> 37:12.960
I'll turn to
the market regulation bureau then!

37:12.960 --> 37:14.420
The market regulation...

37:15.000 --> 37:16.130
Here's your refund.

37:16.170 --> 37:17.770
Don't ever buy from us again.

37:20.400 --> 37:21.330
Smarten up, lad.

37:24.330 --> 37:24.890
Sis Bai,

37:24.920 --> 37:26.670
this is no way to do business.

37:29.530 --> 37:30.160
That guy

37:30.180 --> 37:31.800
is a notorious troublemaker in this area.

37:31.800 --> 37:32.510
He is very close

37:32.510 --> 37:33.440
with some thugs.

37:34.000 --> 37:35.190
If I hadn't given him a refund today,

37:35.190 --> 37:36.400
he'd probably bring a gang here

37:36.400 --> 37:37.330
to cause a scene,

37:37.360 --> 37:38.840
which would disrupt my business.

37:38.840 --> 37:39.320
Look.

37:39.550 --> 37:40.360
It's torn.

37:40.550 --> 37:42.280
He's just too fat to fit in this.

37:44.760 --> 37:45.710
I really don't want to continue

37:45.710 --> 37:47.170
running a stall like this.

37:54.590 --> 37:55.280
Look.

37:55.670 --> 37:57.480
It seems the sales are going well,

37:57.480 --> 37:59.030
but the profit margins are thin.

37:59.030 --> 38:00.320
And we keep bumping into crazy guys.

38:00.320 --> 38:00.920
Our business works

38:00.920 --> 38:02.110
by making small profits
from quick returns.

38:02.110 --> 38:03.690
All our money is hard-earned.

38:03.690 --> 38:04.690
Rich boy,

38:05.000 --> 38:06.840
are you already exhausted
before we even get started?

38:06.840 --> 38:07.800
No.

38:07.920 --> 38:10.510
I did know the profits would be thin,

38:10.590 --> 38:12.590
but I didn't expect them to be this slim.

38:12.590 --> 38:13.190
That said,

38:13.450 --> 38:14.400
if you guys can stick to it,

38:14.400 --> 38:15.000
I can too.

38:15.800 --> 38:17.440
Actually, I've been thinking.

38:17.440 --> 38:18.070
After

38:18.400 --> 38:19.710
I rent a shop,

38:19.710 --> 38:21.400
what kind of business should I do?

38:21.400 --> 38:22.200
I can't sell

38:22.230 --> 38:23.830
sundry goods forever, can I?

38:24.070 --> 38:25.280
Xiaolan, help me figure something out.

38:25.280 --> 38:26.520
What should I do that will allow us

38:26.520 --> 38:27.480
to take care of each other

38:27.480 --> 38:28.940
in business in the future?

38:28.970 --> 38:30.630
My uncle is transitioning into

38:30.630 --> 38:32.800
a commercial renovation contractor.

38:33.070 --> 38:33.880
I think I'll probably build

38:33.880 --> 38:35.740
a career in that industry as well.

38:36.150 --> 38:37.070
How about I start

38:37.070 --> 38:38.070
a building materials business?

38:38.070 --> 38:38.710
Some stores

38:38.710 --> 38:39.920
near Renmin Bridge sell stuff like those.

38:39.920 --> 38:41.320
But they aren't very big.

38:42.030 --> 38:43.110
That's a good idea.

38:43.370 --> 38:43.850
We can

38:43.880 --> 38:45.150
start with a small store

38:45.150 --> 38:46.370
and gradually expand it.

38:46.370 --> 38:47.000
Then, we'll be able

38:47.000 --> 38:48.110
to form a building supply center,

38:48.110 --> 38:49.000
which will be a one-stop shop

38:49.000 --> 38:50.860
for those with renovation needs.

38:52.280 --> 38:52.840
Sis Bai,

38:53.440 --> 38:55.500
is the goal so big that you're scared?

38:55.510 --> 38:56.110
Not at all.

38:56.440 --> 38:57.590
The bigger the goals are,

38:57.590 --> 38:58.840
the more motivated I am.

38:58.840 --> 38:59.440
Tomorrow,

38:59.440 --> 39:01.190
let's go do some...

39:01.280 --> 39:01.630
What is it called?

39:01.630 --> 39:02.760
That thingy...

39:02.880 --> 39:03.630
Market research.

39:03.630 --> 39:04.510
Yes, market research.

39:04.510 --> 39:05.440
Let's do it together, Wei.

39:05.440 --> 39:05.970
Shall we?

39:07.040 --> 39:08.230
I didn't realize it could so hard

39:08.230 --> 39:09.550
to be a self-employed vendor.

39:09.550 --> 39:10.840
All my youthful years

39:11.120 --> 39:11.920
are being wasted

39:11.920 --> 39:13.180
on such trivialities.

39:14.630 --> 39:16.230
Remember who said youth was about
taking risks?

39:16.230 --> 39:17.230
If you really can't manage,

39:17.230 --> 39:19.230
how about I give Second Uncle a call?

39:19.630 --> 39:20.840
Please don't.

39:21.510 --> 39:22.770
It'll make feel worse.

39:24.000 --> 39:26.070
Xiaolan, why are you so optimistic?

39:26.280 --> 39:27.740
You've never complained.

39:29.230 --> 39:30.000
When these people,

39:30.000 --> 39:31.800
who I strove so hard to befriend,

39:32.320 --> 39:33.630
are around, I always feel the urge

39:33.630 --> 39:35.590
to give them some pointers
based on my knowledge

39:35.590 --> 39:36.630
of the future.

39:37.760 --> 39:38.550
Yeah.

39:38.880 --> 39:40.280
I'm clearly the oldest,

39:40.550 --> 39:42.950
but Xiaolan is the one
acting like a parent.

39:44.920 --> 39:46.710
But I'm worried that I might try too hard,

39:46.710 --> 39:48.640
say too much, and expose the truth.

39:51.590 --> 39:53.990
Children from poor families mature early.

39:54.590 --> 39:57.320
Actually,
I've been having a rough patch lately.

40:18.320 --> 40:19.590
Mr. Yuan, hello.

40:20.300 --> 40:21.220
You are?

40:21.280 --> 40:22.440
I'm Xia Xiaolan, who's been asking

40:22.440 --> 40:24.170
to rent that store on 27th Road.

40:24.810 --> 40:25.550
That store...

40:25.550 --> 40:26.840
I'm not declining your offer,

40:26.840 --> 40:28.480
but the property rights are a mess.

40:28.480 --> 40:29.810
We can't make the decision.

40:29.810 --> 40:30.370
I know

40:30.400 --> 40:31.890
it's co-owned by an individual.

40:31.890 --> 40:33.110
Please tell me about this person.

40:33.110 --> 40:34.710
I'll try to convince him myself.

40:34.710 --> 40:35.800
Comrade Xia,

40:36.030 --> 40:37.070
I find your determination

40:37.070 --> 40:38.070
genuinely admirable.

40:38.070 --> 40:38.600
However,

40:38.800 --> 40:40.130
I really can't tell you.

40:40.490 --> 40:41.110
If that person finds out

40:41.110 --> 40:42.030
that I disclose anything,

40:42.030 --> 40:42.560
I will...

40:43.960 --> 40:45.020
Anyway, I'm sorry.

40:50.590 --> 40:52.120
Who on earth is that person?

40:52.800 --> 40:54.730
Nobody dares to mention him or her.

40:59.230 --> 41:01.440
Gosh, it smells so good.

41:03.920 --> 41:04.320
Mom.

41:04.550 --> 41:05.630
I think I need to hurry up

41:05.630 --> 41:06.920
and open the clothing stores.

41:06.920 --> 41:08.400
Otherwise, when your cooking gets better,

41:08.400 --> 41:10.330
I'll surely become too fat to walk.

41:12.960 --> 41:14.320
This is for Granny Yu.

41:15.670 --> 41:16.670
Ours is in the pot.

41:16.800 --> 41:17.320
Okay.

41:23.150 --> 41:23.960
Granny Yu,

41:24.290 --> 41:25.660
I made pork ribs and steamed buns

41:25.660 --> 41:27.150
stuffed with wild vegetables today.

41:27.150 --> 41:28.030
I'll put them here.

41:28.030 --> 41:29.150
Do have a try.

41:34.190 --> 41:34.920
Granny Yu?

41:36.800 --> 41:37.510
Granny Yu.

41:50.670 --> 41:51.360
Granny Yu!

41:51.880 --> 41:52.630
Granny Yu!

41:53.590 --> 41:54.280
Xiaolan!

41:54.960 --> 41:55.710
Xiaolan!

41:56.550 --> 41:57.350
What's wrong?

41:58.230 --> 41:59.560
Xiaolan, come quickly!

42:00.290 --> 42:00.800
Xiaolan!

42:00.800 --> 42:01.400
Granny Yu!

42:04.000 --> 42:04.730
She fainted.

42:04.760 --> 42:06.000
Call an ambulance now.

42:06.000 --> 42:07.200
I'll go make the call.

42:07.960 --> 42:08.590
Granny Yu.

42:09.400 --> 42:10.110
Granny Yu?

42:13.640 --> 42:14.670
I noticed a couple of days ago

42:14.670 --> 42:16.290
that Granny Yu seemed low on energy.

42:16.290 --> 42:17.880
She usually has tea in the courtyard,

42:17.880 --> 42:20.010
yet she stayed in for the past two days.

42:20.190 --> 42:21.000
This is my fault.

42:21.000 --> 42:22.440
I should have checked on her.

42:22.440 --> 42:22.960
Mom,

42:23.400 --> 42:24.110
this is not your fault.

42:24.110 --> 42:24.840
Don't worry.

42:24.920 --> 42:26.250
Just trust the doctors.

42:27.360 --> 42:27.840
Nurse.

42:27.960 --> 42:28.550
Nurse,

42:28.960 --> 42:30.070
how is the patient?

42:30.150 --> 42:31.680
What kind of family are you?

42:31.920 --> 42:33.280
The patient went into shock

42:33.280 --> 42:34.330
due to ketoacidosis.

42:34.330 --> 42:35.320
She has diabetes.

42:35.320 --> 42:37.280
Have you never paid attention to her?

42:37.280 --> 42:37.740
Auntie.

42:38.550 --> 42:39.590
What did you just say?

42:39.590 --> 42:40.590
She has diabetes?

42:40.630 --> 42:41.230
Yes.

42:41.560 --> 42:43.190
The patient's really old now.

42:43.190 --> 42:44.070
As her family, you should...

42:44.070 --> 42:45.150
Nurse, you're mistaken.

42:45.150 --> 42:46.460
They are Granny Yu's tenants.

42:46.460 --> 42:47.070
It's been less than a month

42:47.070 --> 42:48.150
since they moved into her place.

42:48.150 --> 42:48.960
Nurse,

42:49.110 --> 42:50.800
make sure you try your best to save her.

42:50.800 --> 42:52.460
We will certainly do our best.

42:52.480 --> 42:54.240
The patient needs hospitalizing,
given her situation.

42:54.240 --> 42:55.190
Now, go home and prepare

42:55.190 --> 42:56.760
some daily necessities for her.

42:56.760 --> 42:58.070
Then tell her family to come.

42:58.070 --> 42:58.510
Okay.

42:59.630 --> 43:00.670
You two stay here.

43:00.670 --> 43:01.800
I'll go fetch the stuff.

43:01.800 --> 43:02.150
Mom,

43:02.490 --> 43:03.110
don't go home.

43:03.110 --> 43:04.280
Just buy something nearby.

43:04.280 --> 43:04.710
Okay.

43:05.160 --> 43:05.880
Watch her then, you two.

43:05.880 --> 43:06.280
Sure.
